WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 17=

02:26.670 --> 02:28.270
Good thing I didn't go astray

02:28.460 --> 02:29.486
and make a grave mistake.

02:29.990 --> 02:30.830
Sir,

02:30.990 --> 02:31.830
you must help me out

02:31.830 --> 02:32.626
before Her Grace.

02:32.637 --> 02:33.663
Put in a good word for me.

02:37.860 --> 02:38.700
Sir.

02:40.670 --> 02:41.510
Hey.

02:49.830 --> 02:50.700
These are the decrees

02:50.700 --> 02:52.070
issued by the former Sovereign.

02:52.230 --> 02:53.070
That's right.

02:54.140 --> 02:55.110
Also the second thing

02:55.270 --> 02:56.140
spirits hate the most.

02:57.140 --> 02:58.350
But I quite like it.

02:59.270 --> 03:00.460
So golden and shiny.

03:02.140 --> 03:03.350
Building this wall

03:03.990 --> 03:05.180
cost quite a bit of gold.

03:06.620 --> 03:07.460
Issuing decrees

03:08.580 --> 03:09.746
to bring fortune to the world

03:10.460 --> 03:11.300
is called the Way.

03:13.070 --> 03:14.270
How wise of you.

03:15.740 --> 03:16.790
But most spirits

03:17.110 --> 03:18.510
dislike

03:18.790 --> 03:20.510
these restrictive laws.

03:21.020 --> 03:21.860
When Her Grace

03:21.860 --> 03:22.990
enforced the decrees,

03:23.390 --> 03:24.420
it caused quite a stir.

03:24.900 --> 03:26.270
But she's so powerful.

03:26.540 --> 03:27.489
With a wave of her hand

03:27.500 --> 03:28.300
and a single glance,

03:28.300 --> 03:29.300
she silenced those rebels

03:29.700 --> 03:30.540
forever.

03:33.270 --> 03:34.740
As long as she is the Sovereign,

03:35.860 --> 03:36.990
the Void will be stable

03:38.580 --> 03:39.626
and the Mortal World safe.

03:44.460 --> 03:45.620
(Even if no one knows)

03:47.110 --> 03:47.950
(or remembers.)

04:01.300 --> 04:02.620
I heard that to spirits,

04:03.460 --> 04:04.390
mortals are just prey.

04:05.350 --> 04:07.030
Why aren't these spirits
interested in me?

04:07.300 --> 04:09.300
You carry Her Grace's aura now.

04:09.510 --> 04:10.390
In their eyes,

04:10.390 --> 04:11.420
you're one of them.

04:17.420 --> 04:18.470
You said the Golden Wall

04:18.570 --> 04:20.310
is the second most hated place
for spirits.

04:20.660 --> 04:21.500
So, what's the first

04:21.500 --> 04:22.340
most hated place?

04:23.160 --> 04:24.000
Sir,

04:24.000 --> 04:25.002
why are you so curious

04:25.013 --> 04:25.740
about everything?

04:28.550 --> 04:30.420
The place spirits hate most

04:30.860 --> 04:32.350
is the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

04:33.400 --> 04:34.260
Let's go.

04:34.260 --> 04:35.300
Quick, hurry up.

04:36.180 --> 04:37.020
He...

04:48.940 --> 04:50.550
The Execution Platform

04:50.790 --> 04:52.110
is a sacred place of the Void.

04:52.710 --> 04:54.350
For a mortal like you to go there,

04:54.620 --> 04:55.590
can you withstand it?

04:56.060 --> 04:57.420
It's filled with righteous energy,

04:58.300 --> 04:59.380
and Simu guards it.

05:00.500 --> 05:01.670
Why shouldn't I?

05:03.030 --> 05:04.590
You're not a Starhaven sorcerer.

05:06.030 --> 05:07.670
How can you wield this spirit weapon?

05:09.670 --> 05:11.350
You seem interested in my affairs.

05:12.620 --> 05:14.300
Looking for another way to kill me?

05:18.790 --> 05:20.790
You think I'd do such a thing?

05:20.940 --> 05:21.990
I doubt you'd do

05:22.420 --> 05:23.860
such a reckless thing again.

05:37.180 --> 05:38.420
Simu's patience

05:38.820 --> 05:39.860
has always been limited.

05:40.710 --> 05:41.990
Even the most novel things

05:42.420 --> 05:44.110
quickly lose their appeal.

05:44.380 --> 05:45.380
Your hostility toward me

05:46.230 --> 05:47.230
is all because of Simu.

05:47.940 --> 05:49.710
She's known you for 300 years,

05:50.550 --> 05:51.820
and she still doesn't like you.

05:53.260 --> 05:55.230
You think too highly of yourself.

06:02.550 --> 06:03.590
Farewell, Your Lordship.

06:12.350 --> 06:13.420
What's wrong?

06:16.230 --> 06:18.150
I'm feeling cold again.

06:19.910 --> 06:20.750
Hey!

06:24.590 --> 06:25.430
Maizi,

06:26.230 --> 06:27.150
I'm still cold.

06:28.990 --> 06:30.380
Bring me a few more braziers.

06:31.180 --> 06:32.020
Alright.

06:34.470 --> 06:35.310
Your Grace.

06:42.300 --> 06:43.500
Why did you end up like this

06:43.860 --> 06:45.030
in such a short time?

06:47.230 --> 06:48.300
I just caught some wind

06:49.550 --> 06:50.790
and got a bit of a chill.

07:01.990 --> 07:03.180
Didn't I suppress

07:03.180 --> 07:04.020
the cold poison?

07:04.620 --> 07:05.800
How did it relapse so quickly?

07:06.260 --> 07:08.030
It really isn't easy for a mortal

07:09.420 --> 07:10.590
to stay in the Void.

07:25.860 --> 07:27.180
Why is it suddenly getting warm?

07:29.710 --> 07:30.670
In this Zone,

07:32.030 --> 07:33.670
you can be free from the cold poison.

07:34.910 --> 07:36.380
But you can't leave me.

07:40.740 --> 07:41.580
So, that means

07:43.420 --> 07:44.260
I can stay

07:44.260 --> 07:45.180
by your side openly.

07:50.670 --> 07:52.990
If you dare offend me again,

07:53.860 --> 07:56.030
I'll remove this Zone immediately

07:57.590 --> 07:59.550
and let the cold poison consume you.

08:06.150 --> 08:07.380
Thank you for your great mercy.

08:07.550 --> 08:08.390
You saved my life.

08:21.610 --> 08:22.470
You just need to stay

08:22.470 --> 08:23.790
within ten steps of me.

08:24.420 --> 08:25.620
No need to follow so closely.

09:14.590 --> 09:16.710
Now that you've become spirits

09:16.950 --> 09:18.310
and newly arrived in the Void,

09:18.660 --> 09:21.350
you must strictly obey
the Golden-wall Decrees.

09:27.110 --> 09:28.430
The decrees were established

09:28.900 --> 09:31.590
to govern all spirits in the Void.

09:32.470 --> 09:33.620
From Her Grace above

09:34.070 --> 09:36.660
to ordinary spirits below,
all must comply.

09:37.780 --> 09:39.140
All spirits of the Void

09:39.470 --> 09:41.310
can't enter the Mortal World
without cause,

09:42.310 --> 09:43.780
can't harm or kill mortals

09:44.310 --> 09:45.470
without reason,

09:46.070 --> 09:47.780
can't meddle in Mortal World affairs,

09:48.620 --> 09:50.140
can't incite unrest or rebellion,

09:50.830 --> 09:51.803
and can't commit treason.

09:53.190 --> 09:54.660
During curfew, those without a token

09:55.140 --> 09:56.110
may not venture outside.

09:57.620 --> 09:59.430
Remember the pain you just felt.

10:00.190 --> 10:01.950
If you violate the Golden-wall Decrees,

10:02.190 --> 10:03.540
the punishment you'll receive

10:04.310 --> 10:07.020
will be a thousand times worse.

10:09.540 --> 10:10.660
You enforce the law

10:10.660 --> 10:11.900
with unwavering dedication,

10:12.830 --> 10:14.230
never once slacking in 300 years.

10:14.780 --> 10:15.640
The decrees

10:15.660 --> 10:17.380
have endured in the Void to this day

10:17.990 --> 10:19.710
thanks to your efforts.

10:20.900 --> 10:22.350
Her Grace enforces the decrees

10:22.500 --> 10:24.230
to honor the previous Sovereign's will.

10:24.950 --> 10:26.140
You're always consistent

10:26.140 --> 10:27.230
and swift in action.

10:28.350 --> 10:30.190
We're pale in comparison.

10:35.020 --> 10:36.310
Whatever Simu wants,

10:36.860 --> 10:38.710
I will make it happen for her.

10:40.900 --> 10:42.740
(Xu)

10:43.430 --> 10:44.270
Xuling Temple.

10:44.540 --> 10:45.380
Good.

10:47.380 --> 10:48.220
Next.

10:53.860 --> 10:54.700
Jiling Temple.

10:56.540 --> 10:57.380
Next.

10:58.530 --> 10:59.720
Excavating North Abyss.

11:00.140 --> 11:01.662
The Right Hand wants to recruit spirits

11:01.673 --> 11:02.830
to excavate North Abyss.

11:03.070 --> 11:04.660
Since we're all here in the Void…

11:04.660 --> 11:05.500
30,000 spirit stones.

11:05.780 --> 11:06.673
So many.

11:06.684 --> 11:07.630
I should give it a try.

11:08.590 --> 11:10.310
There's no such easy fortune.

11:10.660 --> 11:12.260
What about your life?

11:13.110 --> 11:14.260
Look at what's written there.

11:14.620 --> 11:16.260
(Notice)
This won't be easy.

11:16.780 --> 11:17.710
I still have to go.

11:24.430 --> 11:25.270
Come in.

11:42.070 --> 11:43.860
I have urgent matters for Her Grace.

11:44.260 --> 11:45.100
Others

11:45.470 --> 11:46.310
should leave.

11:47.380 --> 11:48.220
My apologies.

11:48.430 --> 11:49.676
I can't leave even if I want to.

11:52.110 --> 11:52.950
Go ahead.

11:57.990 --> 11:58.830
All new spirits

11:58.830 --> 12:00.110
have been registered.

12:00.540 --> 12:01.830
Recruitment for the excavation

12:02.070 --> 12:03.190
is proceeding as planned.

12:03.660 --> 12:05.190
Yet all temples have failed

12:05.500 --> 12:07.190
in spirit ascension.

12:09.540 --> 12:10.540
What a loyal

12:10.693 --> 12:11.666
and diligent subordinate.

12:11.900 --> 12:12.740
Your Lordship…

12:18.140 --> 12:19.620
Spirits are born from obsession.

12:20.190 --> 12:21.030
Having them

12:21.030 --> 12:23.070
willingly let go and enter the pool

12:23.070 --> 12:24.140
won't be easy.

12:24.710 --> 12:25.850
We'll need more time

12:25.900 --> 12:26.900
to plan this carefully.

12:27.590 --> 12:30.110
Spirit ascension is the righteous path.

12:30.877 --> 12:32.470
We can't give up just because it's hard.

12:33.070 --> 12:34.350
This can't be rushed.

12:35.070 --> 12:36.540
Discuss it more with Jiang Ai.

12:37.430 --> 12:38.270
Yan,

12:39.070 --> 12:40.129
you've worked hard lately.

12:40.590 --> 12:41.710
Go back and get some rest.

12:44.780 --> 12:45.620
Then,

12:47.310 --> 12:48.830
I'll take him with me as well.

12:50.950 --> 12:51.900
As for the rest,

12:53.190 --> 12:54.260
I'll oversee it.

13:00.430 --> 13:01.270
Yes.

13:09.780 --> 13:10.620
Speak.

13:11.110 --> 13:12.310
What were you about to say?

13:46.530 --> 13:52.390
♪Touched memories linger like shadows♪

13:53.020 --> 13:58.530
♪Scattered reflections
sink into my heart♪

13:59.120 --> 14:05.130
♪If I could softly call you like this♪

14:06.220 --> 14:10.830
♪As gentle as a fleeting embrace♪

14:12.330 --> 14:17.980
♪Though apart, my thoughts still swirl♪

14:18.600 --> 14:24.220
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

14:24.750 --> 14:28.110
♪There are passions and pains♪

14:28.310 --> 14:31.210
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

14:31.890 --> 14:38.120
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

14:39.430 --> 14:42.190
♪Even if the day gives way to night♪

14:42.190 --> 14:43.840
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

14:43.840 --> 14:46.670
♪What would come of it?♪

14:47.080 --> 14:48.580
♪I care for no one but you♪

14:48.580 --> 14:50.230
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

14:50.230 --> 14:53.410
♪To heal the deepest wounds♪

14:53.930 --> 14:56.620
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

14:56.620 --> 14:59.370
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

14:59.610 --> 15:01.970
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

15:01.970 --> 15:05.940
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

15:36.220 --> 15:39.220
(Sovereign's Hall)

15:52.020 --> 15:52.860
I knew him.

15:53.230 --> 15:54.470
Her Grace favors him now.

15:54.830 --> 15:55.650
Let me in,

15:55.661 --> 15:56.990
and I won't hold this against you.

15:59.900 --> 16:01.526
I'm a generous person.

16:01.537 --> 16:02.617
I'll let you off this time.

16:03.110 --> 16:04.500
I'll just wait for him outside.

16:04.500 --> 16:05.470
I won't go in anymore.

16:06.020 --> 16:07.110
Put me down!

16:17.310 --> 16:18.150
A mortal.

16:18.660 --> 16:19.710
He's following Her Grace.

16:21.950 --> 16:23.230
He smells so good.

16:26.140 --> 16:26.980
A mortal.

16:52.540 --> 16:53.430
(His obsession)

16:54.140 --> 16:55.620
(is probably to live a warm life.)

16:56.780 --> 16:57.620
(This person)

16:58.860 --> 17:00.070
(must be afraid of water.)

17:03.020 --> 17:04.390
(The Lords of the 24 Temples)

17:05.260 --> 17:06.260
(truly are)

17:06.670 --> 17:07.580
(unique.)

17:09.340 --> 17:10.470
I never expected Her Grace

17:10.470 --> 17:11.710
to choose such a pretty boy.

17:11.710 --> 17:12.550
He's so scrawny.

17:12.550 --> 17:14.060
I could crush several with one hand.

17:14.470 --> 17:16.060
I think he looks fine.

17:16.430 --> 17:17.300
His appearance

17:17.300 --> 17:18.670
only falls a bit short of mine.

17:36.580 --> 17:37.420
Young man.

17:48.500 --> 17:49.340
Young man,

17:49.820 --> 17:51.540
Her Grace brought you here.

17:51.830 --> 17:52.912
The former Sovereign's wife

17:52.923 --> 17:53.740
never even came here.

17:55.340 --> 17:56.260
You flatter me.

17:56.740 --> 17:58.150
Her Grace and I had no choice.

17:58.580 --> 17:59.710
What are you saying?

18:00.100 --> 18:01.580
If Her Grace didn't want to,

18:01.580 --> 18:02.870
who could force her?

18:04.060 --> 18:05.710
I feel sorry for the Right Hand.

18:06.150 --> 18:07.670
This pretty boy was brought here.

18:08.500 --> 18:09.430
Are we going to have

18:09.580 --> 18:10.420
a wedding feast?

18:11.060 --> 18:12.910
Then I must dress up nicely.

18:21.740 --> 18:23.190
Lords present today,

18:26.780 --> 18:28.230
what matters do you wish to report?

19:01.540 --> 19:03.190
I dare not deceive you.

19:03.430 --> 19:04.423
That mortal's cold poison

19:04.580 --> 19:05.630
has indeed flared up.

19:06.540 --> 19:08.740
I heard Her Grace used a Zone

19:09.100 --> 19:10.470
to protect him from it.

19:11.230 --> 19:12.070
But

19:13.150 --> 19:15.670
he must stay close to Her Grace.

19:17.990 --> 19:19.430
Keep a close watch on him.

19:20.020 --> 19:21.540
Keep me updated anytime.

19:21.950 --> 19:22.910
Yes, yes.

19:26.230 --> 19:28.020
You'd protect

19:29.740 --> 19:31.740
an ordinary mortal to this extent?

19:37.710 --> 19:38.910
Who has angered you

19:38.910 --> 19:40.340
to such an extent?

19:55.710 --> 19:58.670
What brings you here?

19:59.020 --> 20:01.230
You always tend to Her Grace's needs.

20:01.870 --> 20:03.150
I heard the mortal young man

20:03.150 --> 20:04.580
she brought back

20:04.870 --> 20:06.260
is suffering from cold poison,

20:06.670 --> 20:08.630
causing her great distress.

20:09.260 --> 20:11.020
I happen to have a Cloud Tripod

20:11.020 --> 20:12.230
forged with the South Blaze.

20:12.390 --> 20:13.950
It can temporarily suppress cold poison.

20:14.470 --> 20:16.500
Why not take it to Her Grace?

20:17.390 --> 20:18.910
You're being this generous?

20:21.540 --> 20:23.060
My generosity

20:23.300 --> 20:25.260
naturally comes at a price.

20:27.950 --> 20:28.790
Go on.

20:28.990 --> 20:29.830
On what terms?

20:31.990 --> 20:33.340
Simu wants us to excavate.

20:33.540 --> 20:35.100
Your temple will send Spirit Officials.

20:35.380 --> 20:36.230
Agreed.

20:36.230 --> 20:37.260
After the excavation,

20:37.430 --> 20:38.500
I'll oversee the mining

20:38.710 --> 20:39.670
of spirit stones.

20:39.670 --> 20:40.580
Also agreed.

20:41.340 --> 20:42.180
Deal.

20:43.670 --> 20:44.990
I have one more question.

20:46.150 --> 20:47.820
Do you know of any way

20:48.060 --> 20:49.630
to turn a person into a spirit

20:49.950 --> 20:51.340
or a spirit into a person?

20:54.150 --> 20:56.630
You don't want
to become a mortal, do you?

20:57.060 --> 20:58.780
Seeing Simu likes mortals,

20:59.150 --> 21:01.100
you want to turn back to win her heart?

21:01.990 --> 21:03.630
Mortals are fragile.

21:03.990 --> 21:05.540
How can they compare to spirits?

21:06.430 --> 21:07.950
Who knows?

21:09.740 --> 21:12.500
Perhaps there might be records

21:12.500 --> 21:13.710
in the Starhaven ancient texts.

21:16.390 --> 21:17.230
Back to business.

21:17.630 --> 21:19.230
I agree to the deal we just discussed.

21:19.470 --> 21:20.310
Sign and seal it.

21:24.980 --> 21:26.660
(Yan Ke)

21:42.330 --> 21:43.190
You're paying

21:43.190 --> 21:44.030
such a heavy price.

21:44.260 --> 21:45.190
Are you really removing

21:45.190 --> 21:46.163
the mortal's cold poison?

21:52.190 --> 21:54.190
Once that mortal uses this Cloud Tripod

21:54.190 --> 21:55.540
to dispel the cold poison,

21:56.190 --> 21:57.990
the spirit power attached to the tripod

21:58.430 --> 22:00.230
will enter his organs.

22:01.190 --> 22:03.100
No one will be able to save him.

22:07.870 --> 22:08.820
Thanks, Lady Jiang Ai.

22:08.990 --> 22:09.830
You're so thoughtful.

22:11.990 --> 22:12.830
Simu.

22:26.680 --> 22:27.702
I found a magical artifact

22:27.713 --> 22:29.230
forged with the South Blaze.

22:30.020 --> 22:31.340
Its pure yang and scorching energy

22:31.470 --> 22:32.816
can temporarily dispel cold poison

22:33.800 --> 22:34.640
and help you

22:34.640 --> 22:36.100
avoid trouble from that mortal.

22:38.340 --> 22:39.260
Yan,

22:39.260 --> 22:40.100
how kind of you.

22:40.500 --> 22:41.340
However,

22:41.500 --> 22:42.990
Lady Jiang Ai just gave me

22:42.990 --> 22:44.340
a method to cure cold poison.

22:45.430 --> 22:46.270
Keep the tripod

22:46.740 --> 22:47.710
for yourself.

22:54.430 --> 22:56.300
I sold you the treasure you want.

22:56.630 --> 22:58.300
You never asked me how to cure it.

23:00.540 --> 23:01.390
Simu,

23:01.390 --> 23:02.870
I helped as promised.

23:03.100 --> 23:04.806
Don't forget the spirit stones
you owe me.

23:21.950 --> 23:22.870
Come with me somewhere.

23:30.230 --> 23:31.070
Jiang Ai,

23:31.990 --> 23:33.390
I underestimated you.

23:34.990 --> 23:37.100
The Void's greediest spirit

23:37.990 --> 23:39.740
naturally knows how to scheme.

23:47.340 --> 23:48.180
Your Lordship,

23:48.580 --> 23:50.130
the Left Hand's Spirit Officials

23:50.141 --> 23:51.400
are here for excavation experts.

23:51.453 --> 23:52.639
Their attitude was aggressive.

23:52.820 --> 23:53.780
Should we cooperate?

23:55.580 --> 23:56.740
Of course.

23:57.820 --> 24:00.060
I personally promised Jiang Ai.

24:00.870 --> 24:01.990
Don't let these matters

24:02.580 --> 24:04.340
delay the important business.

24:04.580 --> 24:05.420
Yes.

24:25.983 --> 24:27.093
They say mortals and animals

24:27.104 --> 24:28.236
can't stay long in the Void.

24:29.190 --> 24:30.500
I didn't expect plants here.

24:32.670 --> 24:34.143
The Void is rich in spiritual energy.

24:34.580 --> 24:35.990
There are always blessed things

24:35.990 --> 24:37.100
born from that energy

24:37.100 --> 24:38.390
for spirits to use.

24:39.540 --> 24:40.615
The Crystal Orchid can cure

24:40.626 --> 24:41.560
your cold poison.

24:41.870 --> 24:43.060
It grows right here.

24:50.190 --> 24:51.500
A flower that grows on bones?

24:53.150 --> 24:54.710
Spiritual energy sometimes forms bones.

24:54.910 --> 24:55.925
What grows on those bones

24:55.936 --> 24:56.820
is the Crystal Orchid.

24:57.870 --> 24:58.820
But this one

24:59.190 --> 25:00.300
is far too young.

25:01.300 --> 25:03.340
You need one
that's at least 300 years old.

25:06.710 --> 25:07.630
Even the plants here

25:07.630 --> 25:08.630
live this long?

25:14.795 --> 25:15.670
- Xu.
- Young Master.

25:15.681 --> 25:17.201
- You're finally back.
- Young Master.

25:17.212 --> 25:18.470
We've been waiting for you.

25:22.150 --> 25:22.990
I think I saw

25:24.780 --> 25:26.300
the scenery of Nandu.

25:29.230 --> 25:30.833
This Crystal Orchid can read memories

25:30.844 --> 25:32.100
and trap people in an illusion.

25:32.540 --> 25:33.380
Best not to touch it.

25:45.190 --> 25:46.030
Simu,

25:47.500 --> 25:48.509
all these Crystal Orchids

25:48.520 --> 25:49.180
won't work?

26:12.990 --> 26:13.830
Father.

26:23.610 --> 26:24.840
It's been 300 years.

26:25.060 --> 26:26.700
Why is Father's spirit sense here?

26:27.670 --> 26:28.630
Did he also come here

26:29.300 --> 26:30.500
to cure your mother's

26:30.820 --> 26:31.660
cold poison?

26:40.020 --> 26:40.910
Probably.

26:42.910 --> 26:44.260
It seems that any mortal body,

26:45.100 --> 26:46.300
even Starhaven sorcerers,

26:47.190 --> 26:48.670
can't withstand the Void's cold.

26:51.500 --> 26:52.390
You've asked around

26:52.390 --> 26:53.340
quite a bit about me.

26:54.230 --> 26:55.656
Rather than hearing it from others,

26:56.340 --> 26:57.190
I'd prefer to hear it

26:58.190 --> 26:59.030
from you directly.

27:46.390 --> 27:47.230
Simu.

27:55.300 --> 27:56.140
Simu?

28:03.580 --> 28:04.710
We've searched for so long

28:05.430 --> 28:06.580
with nothing to show for it.

28:09.780 --> 28:10.620
It's all right.

28:11.630 --> 28:13.150
I believe there's always a way out.

28:13.500 --> 28:14.470
We'll find it.

28:16.190 --> 28:17.030
Siwei,

28:18.740 --> 28:19.670
your cold poison attacks

28:19.670 --> 28:20.696
are getting more frequent.

28:21.350 --> 28:22.190
We must find

28:22.190 --> 28:23.580
a cure as soon as possible.

28:26.910 --> 28:28.580
We mustn't let Simu find out.

28:28.910 --> 28:29.870
She'll worry.

28:29.870 --> 28:32.670
Father, Mother, the food is ready.

28:33.430 --> 28:34.270
Coming.

28:35.340 --> 28:36.260
I never knew

28:37.950 --> 28:39.990
Mother once suffered
from cold poison too.

28:42.150 --> 28:42.990
Here.

28:46.380 --> 28:47.230
Here.

28:47.230 --> 28:48.230
This is your favorite.

28:48.230 --> 28:49.910
Prying into my past so easily.

28:50.500 --> 28:51.710
I might punish you again.

28:52.150 --> 28:53.470
A little punishment is worth it.

28:54.430 --> 28:55.430
I got to see

28:55.990 --> 28:56.830
your different side.

28:57.020 --> 28:57.860
Simu, did you

28:58.060 --> 28:59.190
make all these dishes?

29:00.670 --> 29:01.723
Do you think they're good?

29:02.300 --> 29:03.230
Let me try.

29:08.190 --> 29:09.150
Delicious.

29:09.950 --> 29:10.790
So good.

29:12.190 --> 29:13.030
- Here.
- Father.

29:13.300 --> 29:14.140
All right.

29:15.820 --> 29:16.660
Mother.

29:18.630 --> 29:19.470
Thank you, Simu.

29:22.300 --> 29:23.990
Why do you keep going out lately?

29:24.630 --> 29:26.060
Since you've already noticed,

29:26.470 --> 29:27.340
let's tell you

29:27.540 --> 29:28.430
the truth.

29:32.020 --> 29:32.860
Open it and see.

29:37.870 --> 29:38.710
Do you like it?

29:39.150 --> 29:39.990
I do.

29:43.390 --> 29:44.230
Good.

29:44.630 --> 29:45.540
Put the gift aside

29:45.950 --> 29:46.790
and eat first.

29:49.150 --> 29:50.020
The dishes Simu made

29:50.140 --> 29:51.230
- Here.
- are delicious.

29:53.060 --> 29:53.900
Here.

29:56.150 --> 29:57.670
- Alright.
- Your parents loved you.

29:57.670 --> 29:58.740
Thank you, Simu.

29:59.990 --> 30:01.556
They lived with you in the Mortal World.

30:02.020 --> 30:02.860
Have some more food.

30:03.060 --> 30:03.910
Alright.

30:03.910 --> 30:05.300
They hoped you'd live like a mortal,

30:06.060 --> 30:07.390
a real, genuine person.

30:11.300 --> 30:12.140
So what?

30:13.190 --> 30:14.340
It's been too long. Let's go.

30:15.340 --> 30:16.430
Since you won't tell me,

30:17.580 --> 30:18.710
I'll stay in this illusion

30:18.710 --> 30:19.550
and see everything.

30:21.623 --> 30:22.952
Do you know why the Crystal Orchid

30:22.963 --> 30:24.230
dragged us into this illusion?

30:25.780 --> 30:27.150
From the moment we entered here,

30:28.500 --> 30:30.100
it's been feeding on my spirit power

30:30.710 --> 30:31.710
and your soul.

30:35.020 --> 30:36.300
This place is becoming unstable.

30:36.990 --> 30:38.060
It knows we want to leave

30:38.123 --> 30:39.403
and is trying to hide the exit.

30:41.230 --> 30:42.150
I could easily destroy

30:42.150 --> 30:43.230
this illusion.

30:43.910 --> 30:45.196
It holds your father's memories.

30:46.260 --> 30:47.100
Let's keep it

30:47.870 --> 30:48.896
and find another way out.

30:53.740 --> 30:54.700
I can use my five senses

30:55.430 --> 30:56.270
to feel your father's

30:56.270 --> 30:57.260
spirit sense outside.

30:57.740 --> 30:59.100
Perhaps he can help us.

31:50.990 --> 31:51.830
Father,

31:52.870 --> 31:54.020
you helped me, right?

31:54.740 --> 31:55.580
Simu,

31:56.060 --> 31:57.820
have you found the gift I left you?

31:58.740 --> 32:00.190
If you've met someone

32:00.580 --> 32:01.910
very important to you

32:03.230 --> 32:04.670
and brought him here,

32:05.100 --> 32:07.060
this gift is yours.

32:07.780 --> 32:09.020
Follow my spirit sense.

32:09.950 --> 32:11.230
I'll lead you to it.

32:14.020 --> 32:14.860
Father.

32:28.060 --> 32:29.020
I almost forgot.

32:30.950 --> 32:32.005
It's just the spirit sense

32:32.016 --> 32:33.340
Father left behind.

34:28.950 --> 34:29.790
Take a sip.

34:55.950 --> 34:56.486
It needs

34:56.497 --> 34:57.660
to be consumed in small doses

34:57.660 --> 34:58.755
to merge with your meridian

34:58.766 --> 34:59.946
and eradicate the cold poison.

35:01.020 --> 35:01.870
Now,

35:01.870 --> 35:02.910
you can leave my side

35:03.990 --> 35:05.390
without suffering for now.

35:09.700 --> 35:10.540
Simu!

35:33.100 --> 35:33.940
Simu,

35:34.540 --> 35:35.380
are you all right?

35:36.350 --> 35:37.190
I'm fine.

35:37.540 --> 35:38.620
You call this fine?

35:39.540 --> 35:41.020
I've never seen you this weak.

35:43.470 --> 35:44.426
I used some spirit power

35:44.437 --> 35:45.506
to restore the Fusang Tree.

35:46.753 --> 35:47.680
When I formed the array,

35:47.680 --> 35:48.790
I couldn't hold it steady.

35:49.790 --> 35:50.630
No need to worry.

36:24.390 --> 36:25.396
What are you waiting for?

36:25.580 --> 36:26.420
Take him here.

36:27.820 --> 36:28.660
Go.

36:28.660 --> 36:29.500
No!

36:30.060 --> 36:31.500
No, I don't want ascension.

36:31.790 --> 36:33.060
I don't want ascension.

36:42.350 --> 36:43.190
It didn't work.

36:44.470 --> 36:45.790
I told you my obsession runs deep.

36:57.870 --> 36:59.270
While the obsession lingers,

36:59.470 --> 37:00.470
the spirit won't sink.

37:01.430 --> 37:02.950
The obsession must be let go of

37:03.620 --> 37:04.460
willingly.

37:04.620 --> 37:05.460
I don't believe it.

37:06.220 --> 37:07.060
One more.

37:23.180 --> 37:24.500
Who are you

37:25.750 --> 37:26.910
to trespass here?

37:28.180 --> 37:29.180
A formidable spirit here.

37:29.390 --> 37:30.390
What a surprise.

37:31.180 --> 37:32.270
Sir,

37:32.790 --> 37:33.750
who are you?

37:34.220 --> 37:35.950
How dare you ask my name?

37:37.180 --> 37:38.220
This place is forbidden.

37:38.220 --> 37:39.260
You're just a wild spirit.

37:39.271 --> 37:40.627
How dare you speak to me like that?

37:41.220 --> 37:42.750
I know not who you are,

37:43.660 --> 37:45.140
but your vulgarity

37:45.950 --> 37:47.263
is no different from a beast's.

37:47.274 --> 37:48.350
Speak like a normal person.

37:48.350 --> 37:49.190
Lei Qi.

37:49.990 --> 37:51.060
What? Looking for a fight?

37:52.270 --> 37:53.110
Are you stupid?

37:53.320 --> 37:54.160
These spirits

37:54.170 --> 37:55.270
have no way to ascend.

37:55.660 --> 37:56.750
We're not getting

37:56.750 --> 37:57.750
any spirit stones anyway.

37:58.350 --> 37:59.430
No need to stir up trouble

37:59.790 --> 38:00.630
and alert Her Grace.

38:03.470 --> 38:04.790
This is my home.

38:05.950 --> 38:07.310
You shall not trespass.

38:08.870 --> 38:10.220
This is my home.

38:11.430 --> 38:12.700
You shall not trespass.

38:13.830 --> 38:15.100
This is my home.

38:15.950 --> 38:17.750
You shall not trespass.

38:49.310 --> 38:50.150
Where are you going?

38:50.750 --> 38:51.790
Curfew is in effect.

38:54.700 --> 38:55.773
The moonlight is beautiful.

38:56.310 --> 38:57.150
I thought

38:57.910 --> 38:58.750
I'd take a walk.

39:05.430 --> 39:06.270
Let me come with you.

39:11.500 --> 39:12.340
I'd be delighted.

39:13.980 --> 39:16.420
(Sovereign's Hall)

40:33.100 --> 40:35.140
Who knew General Duan
was afraid of heights?

40:38.430 --> 40:39.350
Thanks to you,

40:40.673 --> 40:42.319
I've discovered
another weakness of mine.

40:44.270 --> 40:45.990
Last time I took you flying,

40:46.310 --> 40:47.580
you seemed quite calm.

40:48.500 --> 40:49.870
Last time, you held onto me,

40:51.580 --> 40:52.620
so I wasn't as scared.

40:53.980 --> 40:59.690
♪All things wake, with the east wind♪

40:59.870 --> 41:01.100
From this angle, the Void

41:01.430 --> 41:02.700
looks like an ink painting.

41:03.010 --> 41:07.550
♪In the season at its fullest♪

41:08.480 --> 41:14.220
♪Light the lamps
to pierce the old night♪

41:14.270 --> 41:15.180
Cobblestone paths,

41:16.470 --> 41:17.310
ancient architecture,

41:18.620 --> 41:19.540
weathered walls,

41:23.270 --> 41:24.110
and…

41:24.440 --> 41:27.850
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

41:27.960 --> 41:31.470
♪Savoring wine and graceful dances♪

41:31.680 --> 41:34.110
♪Let me love with all my heart♪

41:34.140 --> 41:34.980
And what?

41:36.430 --> 41:37.270
And Simu.

41:38.970 --> 41:45.670
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

41:45.810 --> 41:46.680
If I were to throw you

41:46.680 --> 41:47.540
off from here,

41:48.390 --> 41:49.416
what would happen to you?

41:51.280 --> 41:52.140
Didn't you say

41:52.140 --> 41:53.180
you liked my skull?

41:54.140 --> 41:55.220
If I fall from here,

41:56.060 --> 41:57.270
my head would split open,

41:58.296 --> 41:59.362
and my skull would shatter.

42:03.540 --> 42:05.140
Then you should thank your skull

42:05.430 --> 42:06.540
for saving your life.

42:08.490 --> 42:11.680
♪Through this life♪

42:11.680 --> 42:15.090
♪In the netherworld♪

42:15.280 --> 42:21.440
♪I see a ray♪

42:23.790 --> 42:26.500
♪To what home shall I return♪

42:33.561 --> 42:38.891
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

42:39.221 --> 42:43.471
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:44.831 --> 42:50.201
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

42:50.501 --> 42:55.101
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:56.191 --> 42:58.031
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:10.241 --> 43:15.681
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:15.861 --> 43:20.191
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:21.561 --> 43:26.951
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:27.181 --> 43:31.121
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:32.891 --> 43:34.781
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:37.441 --> 43:40.601
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

43:40.601 --> 43:43.131
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

43:43.131 --> 43:48.651
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

43:48.651 --> 43:51.891
♪Following fate's guidance♪

43:51.891 --> 43:56.751
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

43:57.091 --> 44:00.111
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:00.111 --> 44:02.931
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:03.191 --> 44:05.721
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:05.721 --> 44:11.141
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:11.311 --> 44:14.381
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

44:14.541 --> 44:19.441
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

44:19.651 --> 44:23.121
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
